Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:08.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N天下統一の道を行く王 嬴政(えいせい)のもと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:08.91,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,By the decision of Ying Zheng, the king that wished to unite all of China,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:12.19,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,the State of Qin began its invasion of the State of Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:12.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国(しんこく)は 魏国(ぎこく)へと侵攻した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:16.57,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The enemy blocking their way is the legendary Great General, Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:16.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ちはだかる敵は\N伝説の大将軍 廉頗(れんぱ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:22.55,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Young generals take on this relentless battlefield in hopes of rendering great military achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:22.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,若き将たちは 大いなる武功を狙い\Nこの苛烈な戦場に挑む
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:32.26,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,In the first battle on the Liuyin Plain,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:34.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,流尹(るい)平野での緒戦 蒙驁(もうごう)の中央軍は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:39.10,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Meng Ao's central army fell prey to the machinations of one of Lian Po's Four Heavenly Kings, Xuan Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:39.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗四天王のひとり 老獪(ろうかい)な玄峰(げんぽう)の\N策に翻弄された
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:45.86,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The Feixin Unit and Yufeng Unit launched a lone counterattack, but failed to make a dent in the enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:45.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,唯一 飛信(ひしん)隊と玉鳳(ぎょくほう)隊が\N反撃に出たが １歩及ばず
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:50.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中央軍は\N大敗を喫してしまったのである
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:50.59,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,and the Central Army suffered a crushing defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:54.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信(しん)）なっ…\N（王賁(おうほん)）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:57.05,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We were completely...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:57.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは まんまと…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:01:00.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まんまと\Nあいつに してやられたんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:01:00.70,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,completely beaten by them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:04.70,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Shit! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:04.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）くそ… くそー！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:09.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\Nこのままでは 軍の士気低下は\N火を見るよりも明らかだった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:09.91,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,It was plain as day that the army's morale would deteriorate given this result...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:14.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:14.45,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:21.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近）飛信 玉鳳 両隊は―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:21.97,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The Feixin and Yufeng Units
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:24.62,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,were undaunted by the enemy's cunning plan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:26.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の狡猾(こうかつ)な策に対し\N１歩も ひるむこともなく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:26.54,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,and crushed it with one valorous attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:29.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勇猛なる攻撃をもって\Nそれを撃破した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.54,0:01:29.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,As a result, the enemy army has fled
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:35.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,and damage to our army was minimized!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:32.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近）結果 敵軍は遁走(とんそう)し―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:35.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が軍の被害は\N最小限に食い止められた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:39.81,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,This can truly be called a victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:39.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは\Nもはや勝利と言って差し支えない！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:45.50,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,In order to prevent loss of its morale,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:45.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）蒙驁軍は\N自軍の士気低下を防ぐため―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:48.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信と王賁の２人を祭り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.25,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,the Meng Ao Army elevated Xin and Wang Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:54.48,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,They emphasized and spread the idea that the fact that the two units made the enemy headquarters retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:52.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人の隊が\N敵本陣をひかせたことを強調し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:54.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吹聴したのである
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:59.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大敗を知る兵たちも\N自らを奮い立たせるべく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:59.21,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The soldiers that knew of the great defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:02.08,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,joined into that fervor in order to cheer themselves up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:02.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あえて それに乗って 歓声を上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:08.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ… これじゃ逆に さらし者(もん)だ\N“敵将逃(のが)したバカ２人”ってな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.70,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It's more like we're being publicly shamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:08.52,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,"Look at those idiots that let the enemy general get away."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:11.59,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Because somebody like you suffered a major wound
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前なんか\N更に深手を負わされてっから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二重に恥ずかしいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.38,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,it's twice as embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:19.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恥ずかしいのは お前の格好だ\N貧乏くさすぎて 皆の士気が下がる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:16.37,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,What's embarrassing is your appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:18.99,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,You look like such a poor hick that it's going to lower everyone's morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:20.78,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What'd you say, asshole?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:20.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…んだと？ てめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:24.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）\N近づくな　今の俺には加減ができぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:24.28,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Don't get close to me. I don't have a lot of patience at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:26.34,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Would you two cut it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近）やめんか！ ２人とも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:28.31,Kingdom-Main,Gramps,0,0,0,,Lord Meng Tian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（じい）蒙恬(もうてん)さま
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:32.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）いいんじゃないの？\N２人の本陣攻撃がなかったら―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:30.30,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,This is okay, isnt it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:32.84,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,If those two didn't attack the headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:35.83,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,the damage from the first battle would surely have been much larger...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:35.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,緒戦の被害は\Nもっと大きかったはずだし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:39.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人には\Nちょっと差をつけられたかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.89,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Looks like those two made some difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:42.13,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Though we never got a chance to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:42.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ\Nこっちは出番なかったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:51.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）少々わざとらしいが\N士気は保たれたゆえ これでよい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.88,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,It's a bit forced, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:51.15,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,but if morale is preserved this way, it's a good thing. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:57.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに わしの２本の剣が動くのは\Nこれからじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:57.35,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Also, my two swords have yet to be unsheathed. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:09.51,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Stay calm... Don't get ahead of yourself, Meng Ao.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:09.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,慌てるな　せくなよ 蒙驁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:15.21,Kingdom - Episode Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs80\be0.25\c&H000000&\pos(638,101.667)}The Thief VS The Strategist
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:20.50,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,On the second day, with the Meng Ao central army having suffered a major defeat in the first battle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）２日目 蒙驁中央軍は―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:24.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,緒戦での大敗を受け\N各隊の再編制を大急ぎで行っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:23.90,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,the various units underwent a hurried reorganization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:27.12,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Get going, Feixin Unit! You're over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:27.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（将軍）\N飛信隊 走れ！ お前らは向こうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:30.17,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I get it! I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:30.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\N分かってる　今向かってんだろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:34.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！ ちゅ… 注目！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.60,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A-Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せくな せくな\N転んでケガするぞい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.33,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Don't rush, don't rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.73,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,You'll hurt yourselves if you trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.88,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,It's General Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）蒙驁将軍だ！\N（兵士）白老さまだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.08,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,The Great White Elder!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:54.12,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,The Great White Elder himself came to inspire us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:54.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）白老さまご本人が\N我らに檄(げき)を飛ばしに来られたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:58.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆に戦術を１つ伝えに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.75,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,I came here to express one strategy to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ 戦術？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.26,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.76,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:10.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守備じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:14.47,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Defense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:14.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水(そすい)）守備？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:17.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）戦場の左右に\N布陣している副将たちも―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:17.91,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,My Vice Generals, who are currently encamped on the right and left sides of the battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まもなく戦いに入る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:20.21,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,will be entering the battle momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:27.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,両軍は 必ず相対する敵を打ち破り\N総本陣まで攻め上がるであろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:24.23,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Their two armies will without a doubt crush the enemies that oppose them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:26.99,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,and then draw together to form a combined headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:30.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,故に その機が来るまで―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:31.90,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Therefore, until that moment comes, us at the center
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:34.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中央の我々は\Nただ ひたすら守りに徹する
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.77,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,must wholly devote ourselves to defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:39.00,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,If I make it through, our victory will be only a matter of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしを守り抜けば おのずと勝つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:44.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）そのためには\N隊が崩れぬよう 必死で戦え
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:45.01,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,For that end, I need you all to fight for your lives to keep your units from collapsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:49.67,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,However, you must be sure to guard your own lives as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）ひいては\N自分たちの命こそ 絶対に守り抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:54.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）よいな？ 我が兵たち
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:54.56,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Understand, my soldiers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が戦友たち
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:58.46,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,My comrades in arms, my brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兄弟たち
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が息子たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.31,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,My sons...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）蒙驁流の檄であった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:11.03,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,That was Meng Ao's style of raising excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:18.64,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,This un-Supreme-Commander-like way of talking shook the soldiers to the bottom of their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:14.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この大将軍らしからぬ語りかけは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:18.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,末端の兵士の心まで\N熱く震わせたのである
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:25.01,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And on this day, the battle began on the wings of the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:25.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして この日\N戦場の両翼で戦いが始まった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.51,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The first ones to move were...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:27.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず最初に動いたのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:29.84,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏国伝令）報告！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:32.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）右軍 姜燕(きょうえん)将軍の隊が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.53,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Jiang Yan's unit in the right army
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:35.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王翦(おうせん)率いる敵左軍と\N戦闘に入りました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.73,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,has entered battle with the enemy left army led by Wang Jian!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:36.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白亀西(はくきさい)）始まったか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.06,Kingdom-Main,Bai,0,0,0,,So it's begun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.81,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Jiang Yan was the one that struck first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）先に仕掛けたのは姜燕将軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:51.36,Kingdom - Titles,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,699.286)}State of Wei Army Right Army General\n\n\n\n{\fs70}Jiang Yan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:58.62,Kingdom - Titles,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,697)}State of Qin Left Army General\n\n\n\n{\fs70}Wang Jian
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:08.13,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Well, the number of soldiers seems even right now. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:07.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）\Nまず 兵の数は互角と見ていい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:11.79,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,But don't underestimate us, Wang Jian. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:11.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 王翦よ 侮るな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:17.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が四天王のひとり 姜燕には\N恐るべき技がある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:17.36,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Jiang Yan is one of my Four Heavenly Kings. He's got some pretty formidable techniques. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（軍長）谷を下るぞ！\N敵の右翼に下から回り込む！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.53,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Descend into the valley!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.64,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We're cutting into the enemy's right wing from below!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）姜燕は 矢で部隊を動かす
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:35.16,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Jiang Yan uses arrows to move his unit. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:39.06,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,And with marksmanship among the ten best in all of China, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:39.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして\N中華で10本の指に入る姜燕の矢は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:41.99,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,his range is twice that of a layman. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:42.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,常人の倍の飛距離を出す
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:50.49,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,As a result, Jiang Yan can direct every one of his units running between mountains at once. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:43.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よって 姜燕は―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:49.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,山々を挟んで走る各隊を\N同時に操ることができるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:53.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）下からも来たぞ！\N（兵士）囲まれている！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:53.34,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We're surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:59.19,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,So to start with, they'll be bewildered by the strength of Jiang Yan's attacks. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:59.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どの武将も\Nまずは姜燕の攻めの強さに面食らう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:05.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このわしでさえ 昔 幾度となく\Nあやつの軍に手を焼かされた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:05.64,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Even I had some trouble with that guy a few times way back.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:10.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通ならば このまま押し殺されて\N姜燕の餌食になるが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:11.11,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Normally, the enemy would just be crushed to death and become Jiang Yan's prey, but... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:17.12,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,I've got a feeling it won't be that easy this time... eh, Wang Jian? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:14.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よもや 今回は そうなるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,のう？ 王翦よ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.52,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Why don't you go show me that talent of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:25.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）あの王騎(おうき)が 間違いなく\N六大将軍級の武将と評したその実力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:28.88,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,that made Wang Qi call you "undoubtedly of the same class as the Six Great Generals". {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:28.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,存分に見せてもらおうか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:31.38,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Urgent report!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:33.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（秦国伝令）急報！\N王翦軍が押し出され始めました
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The Wang Jian Army has started to be pushed back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:36.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の攻勢に前線が崩れつつあります
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:36.82,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The front line is being broken by the enemy's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫(かくきょう)）なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.06,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.71,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:42.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁将軍！\N（蒙驁）フォフォフォ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:48.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,No need to be concerned, gentlemen. Wang Jian is not someone to be done in so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:48.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）皆の者 案ずるな\N王翦の実力は こんなものではない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,う～む…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:58.16,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Urgent report!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:59.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）急報！\N（廉頗）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:02.66,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,There has now been movement on General Jie Zifang's front!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）介子坊(かいしぼう)将軍の前線でも\N動きがありました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）そっちも動きだしたか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.81,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,So he's gotten going too, eh? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:12.92,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Our other target... Huan Ji. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:13.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１人の標的… 桓騎(かんき)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:20.51,Kingdom - Titles,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,695.857)}State of Qin Army Right Army General\n\n\n\n{\fs70}Huan Ji
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:28.31,Kingdom - Titles,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,695.857)\fad(0,900)}State of Wei Army Left Army General\n\n\n\n{\fs70}Jie Zifang
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）報告！\N第１隊 討たれました
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.79,0:08:28.81,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:30.67,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The first unit has been defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかにも多数の被害が…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.83,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Others have considerable casualties as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近Ａ）\Nなに？ …で 後続部隊は？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:33.59,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.44,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Then what about the next units?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:39.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,W-Well, sir, after they slew the first unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:38.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）そ… それが\N敵は 第１隊を討ったあと―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:42.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに退却し 姿をくらましました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:42.07,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,the enemy immediately retreated and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.72,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:45.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近Ａ）なんだと？\N（介子坊）ンンッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:51.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）これが桓騎の戦法である
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.38,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,This is Huan Ji's strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:55.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 正面から敵に当たらず\N山々に分散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.92,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Essentially, avoid hitting the enemy head on by dispersing into the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:09:00.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,潜伏させた小部隊によって\N奇襲攻撃を行うのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:09:00.21,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,and then launch ambushes with small concealed units.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.78,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Once an attack hits an unguarded enemy, they immediately withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:06.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,虚を突いて襲撃しては すぐにひく\Nこれを昼夜を問わず繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:06.28,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,They then repeat this strategy throughout the day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.97,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And on occasion when a State of Wei army enters their midst
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:09.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして\N時折 深入りする魏国軍があれば
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:13.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってましたとばかりに\N集団で これを殲滅(せんめつ)した
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:14.01,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,they attack en masse and annihilate them as if they were waiting for them to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:17.63,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Jie Zifang wore a brave face as this news came to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:17.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勇猛をもって\N聞こえた介子坊であったが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:21.43,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,but this irregular attack frustrated him internally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:21.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この変則的な攻撃には頭を悩ませた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その後 中央軍と王翦軍―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.00,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,After this, the Central Army and Wang Jian Army
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それぞれの戦いは\N膠着(こうちゃく)状態となったが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:30.12,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,were in a deadlock in each of their battles
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:34.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桓騎の軍からは\N連日 勝利の報告が入っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:34.21,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,while the Huan Ji Army reported victory multiple days in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:36.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして ４日目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.61,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And then, on the fourth day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.01,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:38.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（秦国伝令）報告！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:43.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桓騎将軍の隊が またも\N敵補給部隊を襲撃いたしました
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.51,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Huan Ji's unit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.30,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,has once again attacked the enemy's supply unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:46.60,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That very much sounds like one of General Huan Ji's battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:46.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）誠に桓騎将軍らしい戦い
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:49.86,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I can practically see the enemy generals' perplexed faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:50.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵将の困り果てた顔が\N見えるようです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:54.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こういう策では\N盗賊の出という過去が生きますなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:54.49,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,His origins as a thief really shine through in plans like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:02.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… 申し訳ございません
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:01.96,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,My humblest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:04.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,口が滑りました\N（蒙驁）よい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:03.69,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A slip of the tongue...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:04.91,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:09.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗が このまま 手をこまねいて\N見ているわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:09.57,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Lian Po isn't going to just sit back and watch this happen much longer. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:12.83,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,He's bound to present some new move soon... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:12.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ新たな動きを見せるころ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:17.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃが この戦 是が非でも\N勝たなくてはならんのじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:18.14,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,But we must win this war by any means necessary. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:20.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼んだぞ 桓騎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:20.72,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Huan Ji. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:25.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（摩論(まろん)）ハハハハッ…\Nお頭！ 今回も大漁ですぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:26.18,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Boss, we've got a big catch today, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:30.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（桓騎）フッ…\N（魏兵）クッ… お… おのれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.43,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:35.31,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Using nothing buy cowardly tactics... you State of Qin monkeys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:35.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）卑怯(ひきょう)なマネばかりしおって\N秦国の猿が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:38.19,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,Shut your face, worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:38.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせえよ 虫けらが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… ヒイッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黒桜(こくおう)）フッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さ～て…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:50.80,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,All right then, I think it's about time we delivered our present...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:51.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ贈り物が届くころかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:59.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N実は 介子坊を悩ませているのは\N奇襲攻撃だけではなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:59.29,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,It was actually not only the ambushes that made Jie Zifang worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:00.94,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:04.70,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,He-He sent another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近Ｂ）\Nま… また送られてきたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その者は？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.59,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）２日前に\N行方が分からなくなっていた―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:11.73,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's the eighth unit's Thousand-Man General that went missing two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第８部隊の千人将です
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.09,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,What is in the bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:16.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（介子坊）袋の中身は？\N（魏兵）はっ… これは その…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.55,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Well, sir, these are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:19.32,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Open them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:20.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開いて見せよ\N（側近Ａ）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.11,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:23.06,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It may be best not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:24.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここでは やめたほうが…\N（側近Ａ）ジャマだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:23.86,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ！\N（魏兵たち）アア…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:39.06,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,All of those bags are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（介子坊）あの袋 全てが…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:43.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）報告！ 再び荷が…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:41.48,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.04,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Another package has...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:44.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近Ｂ）な… 中身は…\N（介子坊）もうよい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:44.32,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,T-The contents are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.13,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:52.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常 このような非道な行為は\N敵の士気を上げてしまうが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:52.15,Kingdom-Thought,Jie,0,0,0,,Normally terrible acts like this would have the adverse effect of actually raising the enemy's morale, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツのは度を過ぎている
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:54.42,Kingdom-Thought,Jie,0,0,0,,but he is going too far. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:58.93,Kingdom-Thought,Jie,0,0,0,,If I'm being honest, the fact that he's gone this far {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正直 ここまで やられると―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:12:01.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に 兵たちの中に\N桓騎に対して恐怖心が生まれる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:01.96,Kingdom-Thought,Jie,0,0,0,,actually has instilled fear towards Huan Ji in some soldiers. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:05.85,Kingdom-Thought,Jie,0,0,0,,He's a difficult opponent to combat... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:05.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やりにくい相手だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.16,Kingdom-Thought,Jie,0,0,0,,Huan Ji the Beheader. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:10.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（介子坊）“首切り桓騎”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.84,Kingdom - Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fs50\be0.5\pos(375.2,409.467)}Huan Ji
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.15,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,What are you struggling so much with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:32.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玄峰）何を手こずっておるか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.98,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,You're the man they call Lian Po's right arm, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:35.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“廉頗の右腕”といわれた男が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.73,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,doing such a thing is unworthy of the name head of the Four Heavenly Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:39.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,四天王筆頭の名が泣くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.40,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Lord Xuan Feng!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（介子坊）玄峰さま！\N（玄峰）フッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:46.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）玄峰将軍？\N（魏兵）玄峰将軍だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:44.45,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Xuan Feng!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.30,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Xuan Feng!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:51.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玄峰さま　何ゆえ ここへ？\N（玄峰）うむ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:50.41,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Lord Xuan Feng, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:56.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この左軍の実権\Nしばし わしが預かるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:56.52,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,It seems I have been given power over this left army for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.84,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Is this our lord's orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:06.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殿のご指示ですか？\N（玄峰）うむ… まあ 気を落とすな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.99,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,Well, don't get too down about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:09.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おぬしの力を疑ってのことではない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:09.31,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,He doesn't doubt your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:14.59,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,But if this left army is slow going, it will resonate with the entire battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:14.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ ここ左軍がもたつけば\N全体の戦いに響く
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:18.49,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,He wants us to end things quickly and move on to the next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“さっさと終わらせて\N次に進め”とのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:22.70,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,But for you, someone whose skill lies in frontal attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:22.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃが\N正攻法を得意とするおぬしと―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:26.05,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,that peculiar tactician Huan Ji isn't a good fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:26.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クセのある桓騎は\N相性が悪そうじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:29.92,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,I see. So that is why he chose you, Lord Xuan Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:30.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど… それで 玄峰さまが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:33.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,策士には策士というわけですね？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.37,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,A tactician to match a tactician, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:38.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… 一緒にするな\N精神攻撃など薄っぺらいわい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.99,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,Don't lump me with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:39.04,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,Mental attacks are paper-thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:44.81,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,I'll teach that man what the weight of a true tactic is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:44.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが 本物の軍略の\N重さというものを教えてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:50.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… まあ こんなもんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:50.03,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,Well, that oughta do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:51.46,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:58.37,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,Tell those guys about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:58.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（桓騎）\Nこの場所をヤツらに教えてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（黒桜）あいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:13:59.66,Kingdom-Main,Hei,0,0,0,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（丈虎）お頭！\N（桓騎）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（丈虎）敵の本軍が動いたらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:05.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Apparently the enemy's main army's on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.44,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,And it looks like where they're going is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:09.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,向かっている先は\Nどうやら 俺たちの本陣だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,our headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（桓騎）妙だな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:14.64,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:19.40,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,I thought the headquarters was hidden in a place where guys like them wouldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:19.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本陣は あいつらごときには\N見つからぬ場所に隠したはずだが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:22.37,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Also, I've got a report from some spies
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:22.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（丈虎）\Nそれが 間者からも報告があって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:25.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやら\N敵左軍の将が玄峰に代わったらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:25.79,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,and it turns out they swapped the general of the enemy left army out for Xuan Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:30.67,Kingdom-Main,Hei,0,0,0,,The guy that murdered the central army on the first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:30.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初日に中央軍をやったヤツか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:34.73,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Xuan Feng is the best strategist Lian Po has under him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雷土(らいど)）\N玄峰は廉頗配下随一の軍略家だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:36.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:36.22,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:51.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玄峰）\Nヤツの作戦には 致命的な穴がある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:50.88,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,His plan has a fatal flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:54.70,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,With the Huan Ji Army's power dispersed into small units,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玄峰）\N桓騎軍は 軍力を小さく分散し―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:58.49,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,they're like flies hovering around the State of Wei Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:58.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏国軍の周りを\N飛び回っておるハエじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:03.05,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,And by sending around corpses and such, he's lowering our morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:02.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 死体を送りつけるなどして\Nこちらの士気を下げ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:07.50,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,Then he combines his units in places where it's particularly low and attacks as a large army.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:07.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下げきったところで合体し\N大軍で襲ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:11.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃが 悠長すぎるわ 阿呆(あほう)め
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:11.26,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,But he's too damn easy-going, that fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.72,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,If his army is dispersed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玄峰）軍が散っておるなら\Nこちらは遠慮なく―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.99,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,then we don't hold back,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:17.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツの本陣を襲撃 壊滅させる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.24,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,we attack and destroy their headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:20.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その一手で ここの戦は終わりじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:20.61,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,With that one move, we'll end the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:23.20,Kingdom-Flashback,Jie,0,0,0,,Turning the tables on his plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:24.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツの策を逆手に…\N（側近Ｂ）し… しかし―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:27.77,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,B-But Huan Ji's headquarters entered the mountains at the start of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:27.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開戦と同時に\N桓騎の本陣は山に入り
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:30.20,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,We haven't heard a thing about it since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:30.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以来 所在が分かっていません
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.67,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Though we have searched for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:34.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々も ずっと捜しているのですが\N（玄峰）じゃろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:40.24,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,Indeed. He is enacting his plan under the supposition that we won't find his headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:40.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツは本陣が見つからぬと想定して\N今の作戦を展開している
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:43.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こういうものは捜しても見つからぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.62,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,But that's not something you'll find by looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:49.13,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,We {/i1}infer{/i0} it from the lay of the land, the position of their army, and the direction they are attacking from.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:48.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玄峰）地形と こちらの軍の配置\Nヤツらの攻撃している位置から…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:50.76,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:50.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,読む！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:55.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玄峰）\Nここじゃ　ここに桓騎の本陣がある
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:55.05,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,This is where Huan Ji's headquarters is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:59.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,介子坊　本軍を率いて\Nヤツの首を狩ってまいれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:59.28,Kingdom-Flashback,Xuan,0,0,0,,Jie Zifang, lead your main army and hunt down his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:00.26,Kingdom-Flashback,Jie,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:09.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがです 玄峰さま
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:09.16,Kingdom-Thought,Jie,0,0,0,,An acute analysis as always, Lord Xuan Feng. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:11.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つけたぞ 桓騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.65,Kingdom-Thought,Jie,0,0,0,,I found you, Huan Ji! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.53,Kingdom-TL Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,Flags - Huan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:18.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,交戦の構え…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:18.11,Kingdom-Thought,Jie,0,0,0,,They're in position to resist us. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:21.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我らが迫っているのを\N察していながら―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:24.25,Kingdom-Thought,Jie,0,0,0,,I have to give them credit for having the guts to sense us coming, but not run. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:24.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げなかった度胸は認めてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.79,Kingdom-Thought,Jie,0,0,0,,I will not hold back. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,存分に やるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:30.45,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Everyone, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:30.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆の者 いくぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）伝令！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:42.81,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A message!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.81,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A report for Lord Xuan Feng!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玄峰さまに報告！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:50.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,介子坊さま本軍が\N敵本陣に襲いかかったもようです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:50.31,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It appears that Lord Jie Zifang's main army has attacked the enemy headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.35,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Oh! Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:55.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお 早くも！\Nさすが 玄峰さまの読みどおりに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:54.86,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, Lord Xuan Feng's inference was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ならば 終わりじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.82,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,Then it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:17:03.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,剣が交われば ここから桓騎が\Nこざかしい策を弄してもムダじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:17:03.22,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,No matter what little schemes Huan Ji tries to pull now, it's meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:07.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえ ヤツらに\N多少の武勇があったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:07.15,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,Even if he is a bit brave...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.83,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,he will not make it past Jie Zifang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玄峰）介子坊には通じぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:14.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オリャー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:31.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何しろ あの男の\N敵を破壊する力は 廉頗に匹敵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:30.69,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,In any case, that man's ability to destroy his enemies is on par with Lian Po's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.15,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何じゃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:42.69,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,Why do you messengers wear armor with blood on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:40.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玄峰）\Nなぜ伝令係のお前たちの甲冑(かっちゅう)に…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:42.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血がついておる？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:49.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… 目がいいな じじい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:49.25,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,You've got some good eyes, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:12.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玄峰）桓騎か\N（桓騎）そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:10.79,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,Huan Ji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.52,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:15.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言い残すことはあるか？ じいさん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.77,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,Any last words, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:20.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵兵に扮(ふん)して潜入するなど―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:24.53,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,Infiltrating and impersonating enemy soldiers is not something that could be called a war tactic, fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:24.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,軍略と呼べる代物ではないぞ\N愚か者が
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:27.91,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,Much less a general doing it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玄峰）\Nまして 将自らやって来るなど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:32.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… 軍略？ 知るかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.88,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,War tactic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.12,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,I don't give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:36.17,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,I just do whatever makes my opponent angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:36.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（桓騎）俺は ただ\N相手が嫌がることをやるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:40.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（桓騎）\Nそれと 昔から得意なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:40.92,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,And there's one other thing I've been good at for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.93,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,Sneaking in when nobody's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:43.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,留守中に忍び込むのがな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう… フッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:51.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ものを知らぬが\N確かに筋は悪くない …か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.94,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,You may be ignorant,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:51.23,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,but you certainly have talent, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.60,Kingdom-Main,Xuan,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind taking you on as a disciple, Huan Ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:55.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弟子にしてやってもよいぞ 桓騎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:02.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,要るかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.11,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,Like I want your help,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.19,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雑魚が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:14.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひくな！\Nひかずに今の場所を死守しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:11.84,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:14.25,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Protect this place to your dying breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:20.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どの！ 聞こえますか？\N（信）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:19.85,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Lord Xin! Can you hear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.13,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,A gong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:27.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドラの音？\N（楚水）はい　恐らくは敵の
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.04,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:27.81,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,It's most likely the enemy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:35.02,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General, something has happened to the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）\N将軍 敵に何かありましたな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うむ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:42.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）それは 魏国軍本陣から\N発せられたドラの音による情報が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:43.09,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The information the ringing of that gong signaled from the State of Wei Army headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:46.28,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,was delivered to all of the many different battlefields.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:46.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それぞれの戦場に\N伝えられたものだった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:52.20,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Using that signal, the Lian Po Generals were notified at about the exact same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:52.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それにより 廉頗の将軍たちに\Nほぼ同時に知らされたのである
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:57.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,四天王のひとり 玄峰が\N討ち取られたことを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:56.95,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,That one of the Four Heavenly Kings, Xuan Feng, had been slain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:03.24,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,I don't believe it... Lord Xuan Feng was killed?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:00.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎(りんこ)）まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）玄峰さまが討たれた？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:11.82,Kingdom-Thought,Jiang,0,0,0,,Lord Xuan Feng was supposed to be at the headquarters. What is it? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:09.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玄峰さまは 本陣にいたはずでは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:11.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:17.93,Kingdom-Thought,Jie,0,0,0,,Th... That... can't be... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:18.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そんな… バカな…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:26.37,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It appears that Huan Ji disappeared after he slayed Lord Xuan Feng!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏国伝令）玄峰さまを\N討ち取った桓騎は―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:26.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのまま 姿を\Nくらましたもようです
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:28.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに？ す… すると―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.70,Kingdom-Main,Bai,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:31.85,Kingdom-Main,Bai,0,0,0,,Th-Then is it possible that Huan Ji is targeting this headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:32.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桓騎は この本陣を\N狙っているとも考えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:32.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒイッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:41.59,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,You've done it now, Huan Ji... State of Qin Army... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:41.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やってくれたな 桓騎！ 秦国軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:47.44,Kingdom-Main,Bai,0,0,0,,L-Let's temporarily retreat the generals and plan a regrouping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:47.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,か… 各将を 一度 ひかせて\N立て直しを図りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:49.03,Kingdom-Main,Lain,0,0,0,,No need!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:49.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）必要ない\N（白亀西）なっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.52,Kingdom-Main,Lain,0,0,0,,The sun will set soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じきに日が暮れる\N各軍 そのまま野営させよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.46,Kingdom-Main,Lain,0,0,0,,Have the various armies make camp where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:55.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（白亀西）廉頗将軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.10,Kingdom-Main,Bai,0,0,0,,General Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:57.85,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,With the loss of Xuan Feng,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）玄峰の損失で\N少々 戦い方を考えねばならん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:21:00.59,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I'll have to think a bit about how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:03.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かあったら 知らせに来い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:03.26,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,If anything happens, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:09.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）許せ 玄峰…\Nつまらぬ死に方をさせた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.61,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Xuan Feng. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:09.38,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,I let you die a boring death... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:12.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦場で生ぬるいことは言えぬが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:12.67,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,I can't say anything too soft while I'm on the battlefield, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:16.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれだけ共に\N死線を越えてきた うぬを失うとは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:16.81,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,but losing you after we faced death together so many times is... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:21.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 寂しがることはないぞ 玄峰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:21.33,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,But there's no reason to feel lonely, Xuan Feng. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:27.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに 秦国兵の骸(むくろ)で\Nそっちをあふれ返してやるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:27.43,Kingdom-Thought,Lian,0,0,0,,Soon that side will be flooded with the corpses of State of Qin soldiers! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:38.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで緒戦の借りは…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:38.27,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Now, the deficit from the first battle has been... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:42.92,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,No, I'm a move ahead now, Lian Po. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:42.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや これで\Nわしが一手 先んじたぞ 廉頗よ
